SaveName: Battlestar Galactica + All Expansions + 95 Additional Characters
Rules:
This build is primarily for playing with all expansions, but everything is included to play the base game or any previous version. If using all expansions, the extra cards in the top-left on the Rebel Basestar (except the Human/Cylon Allegiance Card) can be deleted.

In addition to fan-made characters, there are also fan-made "You Are A Cylon" cards which can optionally be shuffled in to the loyalty deck. A reference sheet is provided to make building the loyalty deck easy.

The updated lines of succession for all 107 characters are provided on the bottom-left of the board. A quick-reference sheet for the die rolls & basestar damage is in the top-right, as well as the rules for Allies For All Seasons, which is a fan-made variant for using the allies from the Exodus expansion even when you don't want to go to Ionian Nebula.

The complete rules can be downloaded in PDF format from the following links:

https://www.fantasyflightgames.com/ffg_content/Battlestar_Galactica/bsg-rulebook-web.pdf

https://www.fantasyflightgames.com/ffg_content/Battlestar_Galactica/daybreak/BSG_Daybreak_rulebook_engindd_v-3.pdf

https://www.fantasyflightgames.com/ffg_content/Battlestar_Galactica/exodus/rules/bsg-exodus-rules.pdf

https://www.fantasyflightgames.com/ffg_content/Battlestar_Galactica/BSG-Pegasus-rulebook-web.pdf
